snippet.title: El Paso, Elsewhere 'I Want Wealth' Reveal | Summer Games Fest 2022
snippet.description:
STAKES. GUNS. SLOW-MO. Fight demonic puppets through an eldritch meat locker and an Egyptian tomb in the El Paso, Elsewhere debut for Black Voices in Gaming (2022). El Paso, Elsewhere is a new, third-person love letter to classic shooters. Destroy the villain you loved. Neo-noir never looked so good.

STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1546310/
PATREON: https://www.patreon.com/StrangeScaffold
